14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Fitr-sadaqa (zakot al-fitr) — Iyd al-Fitr (Ramazon hayiti) bayramidan oldin har bir musulmon tomonidan to'lanadigan majburiy sadaqa. Miqdori hudud asosiy oziq-ovqat mahsulotining 1 so' (≈3,5 kg) narxi bilan belgilanadi. O'zbekistonda bu bug'doy, guruch yoki arpa. O'zbekiston Musulmonlari boshqarmasining 2025-yilgi hisoblariga ko'ra: minimum ~45 000 so'm (bug'doy bo'yicha) va ~65 000 so'm (guruch bo'yicha) bir kishiga."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Fitr-sadaqa har bir oila a'zosi uchun, jumladan yangi tug'ilgan bolalar, keksa ota-onalar va boshqa qaramog'idagilar uchun to'lanadi. Oila boshlig'i (odatda ota) barcha uchun to'lash mas'uliyatini o'z zimmasiga oladi. Misol: 5 kishilik oila (er, xotin, 3 farzand) × 55 000 so'm = 275 000 so'm. Bayram ertalab namozigacha (namoz al-Iyd) to'lash tavsiya etiladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda fitr-sadaqani bir necha usulda uzatish mumkin: muhtojlarga bevosita (afzalroq), mahalliy masjid imomi orqali, Vaqf fondi (vaqf.uz) orqali, xayriya tashkilotlari orqali. Toshkentning yirik masjidlarida (Minor, Xast Imom, Tinchlik) Ramazonning oxirgi kunlarida fitr-sadaqa qabul qilish uchun maxsus punktlar tashkil etiladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Fitr-sadaqa oluvchilar — bayram kuni uchun yetarli mablag'ga ega bo'lmagan kambag'al va muhtoj musulmonlar. Maqsad — jamoa barcha a'zolari uchun bayram quvonchini ta'minlash. 36 mln dan ortiq aholisi bo'lgan O'zbekistonda, ularning 90% dan ortig'i musulmon, fitr-sadaqa an'anasi ulkan ijtimoiy ahamiyatga ega."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Fitr-sadaqa kalkulyatori oilangiz uchun aniq summani hisoblaydi: oila a'zolari sonini kiriting va mahsulotni tanlang (bug'doy, guruch, arpa) — to'lanadigan umumiy summani olasiz. Kalkulyator O'zbekistondagi dolzarb oziq-ovqat narxlaridan foydalanadi."}]]}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Ko'p beriladigan savollar"}],["$","$L19",null,{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-4","children":[["$","$L1a","0",{"value":"faq-0","children":[["$","$L1b",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"2026-yilda fitr-sadaqa qancha?"}],["$","$L1c",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"Minimum ~45 000 so'm (bug'doy) dan ~65 000 so'm (guruch) gacha kishiga. 5 kishilik oila: 225 000-325 000 so'm."}]}]]}],["$","$L1a","1",{"value":"faq-1","children":["$L1d","$L1e"]}],"$L1f","$L20","$L21","$L22"]}]]}],"$L23"]}]
